      ],
      "content": "<ph id=\"ph1\">[!INCLUDE[wit_nextref](../Token/wit_nextref_md.md)]</ph> does not manage the backup or recovery for data, settings, or applications on mobile devices or computers that you manage with the service."
    },
    {
