      "content": "<ph id=\"ph1\">&lt;a name=\"BKMK_ManagePartners\"&gt;</ph><ph id=\"ph2\">&lt;/a&gt;</ph>Manage partner relationships"
    },
    {
      "content": "If you do not currently work with a partner, you can find one on the <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>Microsoft Pinpoint<ept id=\"p1\">](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=235605)</ept> website.",
