      ],
      "content": "On the <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Subscription details<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> page, in the right pane under <bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt>Partner information<ept id=\"p2\">**</ept>, click:"
